summary: A preset I made over a few years
descriptionHtml:
I find it hard to find mods I like as I have no modding talent. Most of the Presets you see on here are fairly similar and I figured somebody might like this one I made over a few years. It's by no means professional or "complete" but I use it quite often. My PC is pretty poor so the image quality is poor.

If anyone wants to overhaul this preset or make a follower out of it end me a message stating your intent and we can discuss it.
author: Azealous
